Class SpaceObject

java.lang.Object
SpaceObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Debris, RocketBody, Satellite, UnknownObject
public abstract class SpaceObject extends Object
The SpaceObject class serves as an abstract representation of a tracked object in space. It stores shared attributes for objects such as satellites, debris, payloads, or rocket bodies. Subclasses must define the specific type of space object by implementing getObjectType().
